caress,  cears,  ceyes,  cheer,   chide,  chuckle,  clap,  comb,   comfort, 
compliment,  confess,  console,  cough,  cower, cringe, cross, cry, cuddle, 
curtsey, dance,  dream, drool, eh, fart, finger, flex, flip, fondle, frown, 
