grovel, growl, gulp, hiccup, hkiss, hop, howl, hug, hum, ignore, interrupt, 
jump,  kiss, kneel,  knock,  laugh, lick,  liege,  listen,  love,  massage, 
moan,  mosh, muse, nibble,  nod, nudge, nuzzle, pace, pant, pat, peer, pie, 
